\"\n| 150<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snepmusique.com/tops-semaine/top-singles-megafusion/?ye=2019&we=12|title=Le Top de la semaine : Top Singles (t\u00e9l\u00e9chargement + streaming) \u2013 SNEP (Week 12, 2019)|publisher=Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|language=French|accessdate=26 March 2019}}</ref> || 40 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Musica\"<br><small>(featuring [[Ninho]])</small>\n| 39<br /><ref name=\"Week 46\">{{cite web|url=http://snepmusique.com/les-tops/le-top-de-la-semaine/top-albums/?semaine=46?&annee=2019&categorie=Top%20Singles|title=Top Singles (Week 46, 2019)|publisher=Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|language=French|accessdate=19 November 2019}}</ref> || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Du Phoenix aux \u00e9toiles...''\n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Ninja\"\n| 64<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://snepmusique.com/les-tops/le-top-de-la-semaine/top-albums/?semaine=15?&annee=2020&categorie=Top%20Singles|title=Top Singles (Week 15, 2020)|publisher=Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|language=French|accessdate=14 April 2020}}</ref> || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| {{TBA}}\n|-\n| colspan=\"22\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:85%;\"| \"\u2014\" denotes a single that did not chart or was not released.\n|}\n<small>*Did not appear in the official Belgian Ultratop 50 charts, but rather in the bubbling under Ultratip charts.</small>\n\n====As featured artist====\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:24em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|FRA]]<br/><ref name=\"FRA\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Ultratop|BEL<br/>(Wa)]]<br/><ref name=\"WA\"/>\n! scope