d_platin_datenbank/#topSearch |publisher=[[Bundesverband Musikindustrie]] |access-date=25 April 2013 |archivedate=24 November 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124171739/http://www.musikindustrie.de/no_cache/gold_platin_datenbank/ |title=BVMI Germany - Searchable Database |url-status=dead }}</ref>|artist=Pink|title=Get The Party Started|type=single|award=Gold|relyear=2001}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=New Zealand|type=single|artist=Pink|title=Get The Party Started|relyear=2001|certref=<ref>{{cite web | url = http://rianz.org.nz/rianz/oldchart.asp?chartNum=1295&chartKind=S | publisher = [[Recording Industry Association of New Zealand]] | access-date = April 25, 2013 | archivedate = 2013-07-03 | archiveurl = https://archive.today/20130703160652/http://rianz.org.nz/rianz/oldchart.asp?chartNum=1295&chartKind=S | title = RIANZ Top 50 Singles | url-status = dead }}</ref>|award=Gold}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Norway|relyear=2001|certyear=2002|artist=Pink|title=Get the Party Started|type=single|award=Platinum|certref=<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.no/sok/lst_trofeer_sok.asp?type=artist |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105012246/http://www.ifpi.no/sok/lst_trofeer_sok.asp?type=artist |title=Trofeer|publisher=[[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry]] \u2013 Norway|language=Norwegian|url-status=dead|year=2001|archivedate=November 5, 2012|access-date=February 25, 2014}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Sweden|certref=<ref name=\"GLF Sweden - Searchable Database\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/|publisher=Sverigetopplistan. Grammofonleverant\u00f6rernas f\u00f6rening|access-date=25 April 2013|title=GLF Sweden - Searchable Database}}To access certification, one must search (S\u00f6k) for \"So What\" or \"So What P!nk\" and click the \"Visa\" button.</ref>|artist=Pink|title=Get The Party Started|type=single|award=Gold|relyear=2001}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Switzerland|certref=